{"tid":1797242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場有片證實有狗賊由老尖狗屋天台向下方射彈","createTime":"2019-12-25T09:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T02:40:48.000Z","uid":51271,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0c21d500af9839876e675b647fe816174e57f95e","tid":1797242,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:16:20.000Z","msg":"Stand News 立場新聞<br />\n5 mins &middot;<br />\n<br />\n昨晚平安夜，大批市民在尖沙咀一帶聚集，從影片可見，警方於兩分鐘內至少九度從尖沙咀警署天台向地面人群射催淚彈，槍管不停冒出火花。<br />\n<br />\n今年 8 月，《紐約時報》報道質疑，警方於 8.5 驅散市民時，從政府總部高處向地下發射催淚彈，《紐時》引述專家質疑這做法，可能會令非致命的催淚彈變成致命武器；警方其後在例行記者會澄清，當日無派員在高層向下發射催淚彈，「相信係攝影角度問題」。<br />\n<br />\n（片段由讀者提供）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/3394080984045369\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F3394080984045369&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=0ea5b929\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/3394080984045369</a>"},{"pid":"0f8e4d582737274156cef1a4e905555953050f2d","tid":1797242,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fcee79b30caccf93345b8a998d8cb48f6865dad","tid":1797242,"uid":335834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9b4f8a21490758aaa8003589566b0408b26779","tid":1797242,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2bf5c13ff92e676df14bc5f47fe50b10cd2c23","tid":1797242,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:33:13.000Z","msg":"狗賊"},{"pid":"a8a2c0304824bccf7abbc184c7590d7e0e3af69b","tid":1797242,"uid":20348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite